Deploybot is a tool for automated deployments.

It integrates with Atlassian's Bamboo.

The initial version was written quickly.  It is slowly getting better.

Python Dependencies:
* simplejson
* requests
* tornado

Testing Dependencies:
* mock

Ruby Dependencies:
* jasmine gem

Images:

Green checkbar from the Diagona icon set at http://p.yusukekamiyamane.com/.
Deploy spinner from http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Spinning_wheel_throbber.gif.